text: Nazook (also spelled nazuk or nazouk, Armenian Նազուկ) is the name of an Armenian pastry made from flour, butter, sugar, sour cream, yeast, vanilla extract and eggs, with a filling often made with nuts, and especially walnuts. Nazook is sometimes referred to as gata. ==In popular culture== Nazook is often referenced in the 2012 comedy My Uncle Rafael․ ==See also== * Gata (food) * List of pastries ==References== Category:Armenian pastries
title: Nazook
